; Iter 43a: themed level tiles. The first 4 nodes get unique candy+Western
; styling per difficulty:
;   Level 1 PEPPERMINT   (easy)    — white candy + red border, frontier town
;   Level 2 FIREBALL     (medium)  — crimson candy + orange flame border, mine shaft
;   Level 3 JELLYBEAN    (hard)    — mint candy + pink speckle border, farm road
;   Level 4 LIQUORICE    (extreme) — black candy + wood-brown border, mountain pass
; Levels 5-8 stay generic locked (placeholder for future content).
;
; Only LevelNode1 is enabled in v1 (the playable level). Levels 2-4 are
; visually themed but disabled — the user sees their FUTURE difficulty
; progression as foreshadowing.

